    • Uses of Record in net.marfgamer.jraknet.protocol.message

      Fields in net.marfgamer.jraknet.protocol.message declared as Record 
      Modifier and Type Field Description
      Record EncapsulatedPacket.ackRecord
      If the reliability requires an ACK receipt (The name ends with _WITH_ACK_RECEIPT) then this can be used to determine if this is the packet that was received or lost once you are notified through onAcknowledge() or onNotAcknowledge().

      This will always be null before and after the two notifier methods stated above are called.
